name: Protrada  - The Domain Exchange
overview:
Created by Winged Media, Protrada - The Domain Exchange provides real power to domainers of all experience levels with any size portfolio. It makes trading domains as easy as trading shares on the stock market.

Every day over 150,000 domains expire or drop into the domain aftermarket. The Domain Exchangeâ„¢ is a seamless transaction platform and one central place for buying from and selling on the largest domain marketplaces (including Go Daddy, eBay, Sedo and Afternic).

Protrada provides the tools to easily, efficiently and successfully trade on The Domain Exchangeâ„¢. Use Protrada to sort through all those domains to find ones that are undervalued and then bid on an unlimited number of these in the auction process. After winning, choose to set automatic actions including DNS change, re-list for sale or send to a broker. Protrada can also build a site around a domain so the owner may start earning passive revenue while your domains appreciate in value.

Protrada aims to increase not just the success of individual domainers but also the entire domain name investment market. By making the domain name life cycle process easier to navigate and potentially more profitable it is envisaged more and more traditional investors will add this niche to their overall investment portfolio.
